entry.title: Putin, Zelensky Make Rival Visits to Front-Line Troops in Ukraine
entry.content: Both leaders are trying to shore up morale ahead of an expected Ukrainian offensive aimed at taking back territory occupied by Russian forces.

entry.title: Decades of Negligence and Mismanagement Made Turkey's Earthquake Deadlier
entry.content: A comprehensive review shows that widespread problems in the country’s construction boom under the Erdogan government added to the devastating toll.
